script.name: plugin.st.ex.local.report.menu
script.sourceplaintext:
$page.id = get global variable: name='st.ex.pageid' $table.data = get global variable: name='st.ex.report' $menu.data = get global variable: name='st.menu.report'
if $a.event == [MEvent.Start] if not $menu.data $menu.data = table alloc set global variable: name='st.menu.report' value=$menu.data end gosub sub.BuildMenu return $input else if $a.event == [MEvent.Returned] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $menu.id == 'st.report' if $selection == 'clear.all' if $value == [Button.Yes] set stock exchange commodity reports menu item: Enabled=[FALSE] clear table $table.data gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end end end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Group] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $menu.id == 'st.report' if $value remove key $selection from table $menu.data else $menu.data[$selection] = [TRUE] end end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Context] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $menu.id == 'st.report' if $value == 'delete' $selection = string $selection to integer remove key $selection from table $table.data
if not size of table $table.data set stock exchange commodity reports menu item: Enabled=[FALSE] end
gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input else if $value == 'clear' $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1222 $text = read text: page=$page.id id=1228 $input = create input: id='clear.all', message box=$read.text, title=$text, buttons=[Buttons.YesNo], icon=7, default button=[Button.Yes] return $input end end else if $a.event == [MEvent.Switch] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] $value = $a.data[2] if $menu.id == 'st.report' if $value $menu.data[$selection] = $value else remove key $selection from table $menu.data end gosub sub.BuildMenu return $menu end else if $a.event == [MEvent.Finished] end
return null
sub.BuildMenu: $sort.by = $menu.data['sort'] skip if $sort.by $sort.by = 0 $group.by = $menu.data['group'] skip if $group.by $group.by = 0
gosub sub.GetExchanges gosub sub.GetStocks
$WIDTH.ACTION = 60 $WIDTH.TIME = 105 $WIDTH.MAIN = 75 $WIDTH.WARE = 110 $WIDTH.NAME = 185 $WIDTH.LARGE = 95
$menu = create custom menu array
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=909 add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$read.text $values = array alloc: size=4 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1211 $values[0] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=701 $values[1] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=735 $values[2] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=732 $values[3] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1202 add value selection to menu: $menu, text=$read.text, value array=$values, default=$sort.by, return id='sort', width=140 allowtabs=[FALSE] $values = array alloc: size=2 $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104352 $values[0] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104353 $values[1] = $read.text $default = $menu.data['sort.order'] skip if $default $default = 0 $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104351 add value selection to menu: $menu, text=$read.text, value array=$values, default=$default, return id='sort.order', width=140 allowtabs=[FALSE] $values = array alloc: size=4 $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=676 $values[0] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1210 $values[1] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=701 $values[2] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=704 $values[3] = $read.text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=758 add value selection to menu: $menu, text=$read.text, value array=$values, default=$group.by, return id='group', width=140 allowtabs=[FALSE]
if $table.data $sort.reverse = [FALSE] if not $sort.by $sorted.keys = sort table keys: table=$table.data * Sort by column else if $sort.by == 1 $sort.column = 1 else if $sort.by == 2 $sort.column = 7 else if $sort.by == 3 $sort.column = 6 $sort.reverse = [TRUE] else if $sort.by == 4 $sort.column = 2 end $sort.table = table alloc $time.key = get next key: table=$table.data key=null while $time.key $data = $table.data[$time.key][$sort.column] $sort.table[$time.key] = $data $time.key = get next key: table=$table.data key=$time.key end $sorted.keys = sort table keys by value: table=$sort.table end
do if $menu.data['sort.order'] $sort.reverse = ! $sort.reverse
if $sort.reverse $sorted.keys = reverse array $sorted.keys end end
$text.col = array alloc: size=9 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1210 $col.pos = 0 $text = create custom menu column string, position=$col.pos length=$WIDTH.ACTION right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $col.pos = $col.pos + $WIDTH.ACTION $text.col[0] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1211 $text = create custom menu column string, position=$col.pos length=$WIDTH.TIME right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $col.pos = $col.pos + $WIDTH.TIME $text.col[1] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=701 $text = create custom menu column string, position=$col.pos length=$WIDTH.NAME right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $col.pos = $col.pos + $WIDTH.NAME $text.col[2] = $text
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=704 $text = create custom menu column string, position=$col.pos length=$WIDTH.WARE right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $col.pos = $col.pos + $WIDTH.WARE $text.col[3] = $text
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1219 $text = create custom menu column string, position=$col.pos length=$WIDTH.MAIN right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $col.pos = $col.pos + $WIDTH.MAIN $text.col[4] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1214 $text = create custom menu column string, position=$col.pos length=$WIDTH.MAIN right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $col.pos = $col.pos + $WIDTH.MAIN $text.col[5] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1217 $text = create custom menu column string, position=$col.pos length=$WIDTH.MAIN right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $col.pos = $col.pos + $WIDTH.MAIN $text.col[6] = $text
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=735 $text = create custom menu column string, position=$col.pos length=$WIDTH.LARGE right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $col.pos = $col.pos + $WIDTH.LARGE $text.col[7] = $text
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=732 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=$WIDTH.MAIN right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.col[8] = $text add custom menu heading to array $menu: title=$text.col
$i = 0 $size = size of array $sorted.keys
if not $size $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=714 add non selectable menu item: $menu, text=$read.text else $groups = 1 if $group.by == 1 $groups = 2 else if $group.by == 2 $groups = size of array $exchange.array else if $group.by == 3 $groups = size of array $stock.array end
$done.table = table alloc $done.grouping = [FALSE] while $groups dec $groups =
$do.grouping = null if $group.by == 1 if $groups == 1 $do.grouping = 'action.buy' else $do.grouping = 'action.sell' end else if $group.by == 2 $do.grouping = $exchange.array[$groups] else if $group.by == 3 $do.grouping = $stock.array[$groups] end
$i = 0 while $i < $size $time.key = $sorted.keys[$i] inc $i =
do if $done.table[$time.key] continue
$data.line = $table.data[$time.key]
if $group.by == 1 $data = $data.line[0] do if $groups == 1 AND $data != 1 continue else if $group.by == 2 $data = $data.line[1] $data = $data -> get sector $default = $exchange.array[$groups] skip if $default == $data continue else if $group.by == 3 $data = $data.line[2] $default = $stock.array[$groups] skip if $default == $data continue end
$text.col = array alloc: size=9 $data.type = $data.line[0] if $data.type == 1 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1207 $read.text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=21, $read.text, null, null, null, null else if $data.type == 2 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1208 $read.text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=22, $read.text, null, null, null, null else $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=715 end $col.pos = 0 $text = create custom menu column string, position=$col.pos length=$WIDTH.ACTION right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $col.pos = $col.pos + $WIDTH.ACTION $text.col[0] = $text $text = format date: $time.key ingame=[TRUE] $text = create custom menu column string, position=$col.pos length=$WIDTH.TIME right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $col.pos = $col.pos + $WIDTH.TIME $text.col[1] = $text $data = $data.line[1] $exch.sector = $data -> get sector $exch.owner = $data -> get owner race $text = sprintf: fmt='%s (%s)', $exch.sector, $exch.owner, null, null, null $text = create custom menu column string, position=$col.pos length=$WIDTH.NAME right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $col.pos = $col.pos + $WIDTH.NAME $text.col[2] = $text
$data = $data.line[2] $text = create custom menu column string, position=$col.pos length=$WIDTH.WARE right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$data $col.pos = $col.pos + $WIDTH.WARE $text.col[3] = $text
$data = $data.line[3] $text = create custom menu column string, position=$col.pos length=$WIDTH.MAIN right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$data $col.pos = $col.pos + $WIDTH.MAIN $text.col[4] = $text
$data = $data.line[4] $text = convert number $data to string $text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=716, $text, null, null, null, null $text = create custom menu column string, position=$col.pos length=$WIDTH.MAIN right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $col.pos = $col.pos + $WIDTH.MAIN $text.col[5] = $text
$data = $data.line[5] if not $data $text = read text: page=$page.id id=715 else $text = convert number $data to string $text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=716, $text, null, null, null, null $text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=22, $text, null, null, null, null end $text = create custom menu column string, position=$col.pos length=$WIDTH.MAIN right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $col.pos = $col.pos + $WIDTH.MAIN $text.col[6] = $text
$data = $data.line[7] $text = convert number $data to string $text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=716, $text, null, null, null, null if $data.type == 1 $text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=22, $text, null, null, null, null else if $data.type == 2 $text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=21, $text, null, null, null, null end $text = create custom menu column string, position=$col.pos length=$WIDTH.LARGE right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $col.pos = $col.pos + $WIDTH.LARGE $text.col[7] = $text
$data = $data.line[6] if not $data $text = read text: page=$page.id id=715 else $text = convert number $data to string $text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=716, $text, null, null, null, null if $data < 0 $text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=22, $text, null, null, null, null else $text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=21, $text, null, null, null, null end end $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=$WIDTH.MAIN right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.col[8] = $text $contextmenu = create context menu $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1211 add context menu entry: menu=$contextmenu, text='Delete', icon=72, returnvalue='delete', hotkey=null, disabled=[FALSE] add context menu separator: menu=$contextmenu $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1228 add context menu entry: menu=$contextmenu, text=$read.text, icon=66, returnvalue='clear', hotkey=null, disabled=[FALSE] $data = $data.line[1] $exch.sector = $data -> get sector $text = read text: page=$page.id id=301 add context menu global info line: menu=$contextmenu, name=$text, value=$exch.sector $exch.owner = $data -> get owner race $text = read text: page=$page.id id=759 add context menu global info line: menu=$contextmenu, name=$text, value=$exch.owner $data = $data.line[2] $text = read text: page=$page.id id=1213 add context menu global info line: menu=$contextmenu, name=$text, value=$data $text = read text: page=$page.id id=1211 $data = format date: $time.key ingame=[TRUE] add context menu global info line: menu=$contextmenu, name=$text, value=$data
if $do.grouping $default = $menu.data[$do.grouping] if not $default $default = [TRUE] else $default = [FALSE] end
$text = $do.grouping if $text == 'action.buy' $text = read text: page=$page.id id=1207 else if $text == 'action.sell' $text = read text: page=$page.id id=1208 else if is datatype[ $text ] == DATATYPE_SECTOR $exch.owner = $text -> get owner race $text = sprintf: fmt='%s (%s)', $text, $exch.owner, null, null, null end add new grouping to menu: $menu, text=$text, open=$default, id=$do.grouping, indent=null $do.grouping = null $done.grouping = [TRUE] end
$ret = create menu return value: context menu, id=$time.key, menu=$contextmenu, dynamic=[FALSE] add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text.col returnvalue=$ret $done.table[$time.key] = 1 end if $done.grouping $done.grouping = null add end grouping to menu: $menu add section to custom menu: $menu end end end
set menu option: $menu, widthtype=[MenuWidth.Huge] set menu option: $menu, icon=124
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1201 $callback = [Callback.Group] | [Callback.Switch] $player.name = get player name $input = create input: id='st.report' menu=$menu title=$read.text description=$player.name callback=$callback endsub
sub.GetStocks: if $table.data $stock.array = table alloc $time.key = get next key: table=$table.data key=null while $time.key $data = $table.data[$time.key][2] $stock.array[$data] = $data $time.key = get next key: table=$table.data key=$time.key end $stock.array = sort table keys: table=$stock.array end endsub
sub.GetExchanges: if $table.data $exchange.table = table alloc $time.key = get next key: table=$table.data key=null while $time.key $data = $table.data[$time.key][1] $exch.sector = $data -> get sector $exchange.table[$exch.sector] = $data $time.key = get next key: table=$table.data key=$time.key end $exchange.array = sort table keys: table=$exchange.table end endsub return null
